OBINNA EZUGWU Biafran war hero, Col. Joe ‘Hannibal’ O. G. Achuzie (rtd) has reportedly died. Achuzia who was famous for his exploits during the 30-month Nigeria/Biafra war for his air raid was said to have died this morning at the Federal Medical Centre (FMC), Asaba, his home town. He was aged 89. Details later